                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-1470" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS MARSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker. I produce the watch which I re<lb></lb>ceived in pledge of the prisoner on the 26th of Sept.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> What dress had I on? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> A white moleskin dress, but no jacket—it was between four and five o'clock in the afternoon—I swear you are the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I never saw the watch, nor ever had it in my posses<lb></lb>sion. There was a man drinking in the house that day, dressed very much like me; I was at Woolwich all the day.</p>
